      "text": [
        ": «إِذَا غَابَ اَلْهِلاَلُ قَبْلَ اَلشَّفَقِ فَهُوَ لِلَيْلَةٍ وَ إِذَا غَابَ بَعْدَ اَلشَّفَقِ فَهُوَ لِلَيْلَتَيْنِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1917 - Hammad ibn Isa narrated from Isma'il ibn al-Hurr, from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"If the crescent sets before twilight, it is for one night. If it sets after twilight, it is for two nights.\""
